      Table modification data class constructor for changes to existing rows
      Parameters:
      rowData - Row of data from the table containing the changes
      originalRowData - Original contents of the row of data from the table containing the changes
      variableColumn - Index of the column containing the variable name; -1 if no variable name column exists
      dataTypeColumn - Index of the column containing the data type name; -1 if no data type column exists
      arraySizeColumn - Index of the column containing the array size; -1 if no array size column exists
      bitLengthColumn - Index of the column containing the bit length; -1 if no bit length column exists
      rateColumn - Indices of the columns containing the sample rates; null if no rate column exists
